canonical:
  title: 尙書令鷄林公吉禮敎書
  author: 儲元賓
  language: lzh
  text: 敎汝閨庭愛子藩邸重臣當星戶之戒期告成嘉禮念天源之發慶特霈殊恩庶承褒眷之優永協和鳴之兆今差使翰林學士朝散大夫司宰卿直門下省事知制誥兼東宮侍講學士盧旦往彼宣賜某物等具如別錄
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 尙書令鷄林公吉禮敎書
  author: 儲元賓
  language: lzh
  text: 敎汝閨庭愛子。藩邸重臣。當星戶之戒期。告成嘉禮。念天源之發慶。特霈殊恩。庶承褒眷之優。永協和鳴之兆。今差使翰林學士朝散大夫司宰卿直門下省事知制誥兼東宮侍講學士盧旦。往彼宣賜某物等。具如別錄。
korean:
  title: 상서령 계림공 길례 교서
  author: 저원빈
  language: kor
  text: 교하노라. 너는 규정(閨庭)의 사랑하는 아들이고 번저(藩邸)의 중한 신하이다. 성호(星戶 택일하는 일관(日官))가 기일을 정함에 따라 가례(嘉禮)를 이루고, 천원(天源 왕족의 혈통)에 경사임을 생각하여 특별한 은혜를 내린다. 바라건대, 표창하고 총애하는 뜻을 받들어 길이 봉황새가 화합하게 우는 징조에 합하게 하라. 이제 한림학사 조산대부 사재경 직문하성사 지제고 겸동궁시강학사(翰林學士朝散大夫司宰卿直門下省事知製誥兼東宮侍講學士) 노단(廬旦)을 보내어 그곳으로 가게 해서 아무 물건들을 별록(別錄)과 같이 내려 준다.
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0260_020_0090&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Imperial Edict on Auspicious Rites for the Grand Commandant of Gyerim
  author: Chu Yuan-bin
  language: eng
  text: I hereby proclaim to you, beloved son of the inner chambers and esteemed minister of the princely house. As the celestial chronologers have marked the auspicious date, the felicitous rites are accomplished. Mindful of the blessings flowing from the royal lineage, I bestow upon you this singular grace. May you receive these tokens of imperial favor and approval, and may your fortune ever resonate with the harmonious cry of the phoenix. To this end, I dispatch the Hanlin Scholar and Court Official Lu Dan, bearing gifts as recorded in the accompanying register, to convey these honors to you.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The 'celestial chronologers' (星戶) refers to the officials responsible for selecting auspicious dates for important ceremonies.
  - key: ''
    value: The 'phoenix's harmonious cry' (和鳴) is a classical metaphor for marital harmony and dynastic stability.
  - key: ''
    value: This appears to be an official imperial edict of a Korean kingdom congratulating a court official on his betrothal or marriage ceremony.
